getCurrentLocale() - Static method in class dev.b3nedikt.app_locale.AppLocale
The locale currently used by the app.
getDesiredLocale() - Static method in class dev.b3nedikt.app_locale.AppLocale
The locale which should ideally be used by the app. If the locale is in the supportedLocales, it will be used, otherwise we will use the Locale in the supportedLocales which is closest to our desiredLocale. To determine the closest Locale we first search for Locales with the same language and variant. If none exists, we take the first one from the supportedLocales with the same language, if none exits either we just take the Locale.getDefault.
getSupportedLocales() - Static method in class dev.b3nedikt.app_locale.AppLocale
The Locales supported by the app. Usually these are all Locales for which strings.xml files exist.
